		<div class="prose max-w-none">
			<section class="mb-8">
				<h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Professional SEO Services</h2>
				<p class="mb-4">
					Looking to optimize your urban sports website? Our partners at 
					<a href="https://seooptimizers.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
